verbose_text: Nevertheless, the presence of multiple ATAD3B duplications in this study cohort suggests that the duplication of ATAD3B and increased ATAD3B gene dosage alone is not causative of this severe phenotype, but rather the NAHR derived recombinant ATAD3A-C gene and novel protein product generated by the de novo mutational event.
